# plot

```{python}
# Import seaborn
import seaborn as sns

# Apply the default theme
sns.set_theme()

# Load an example dataset
tips = sns.load_dataset("tips")

# Create a visualization
sns.relplot(
    data=tips,
    x="total_bill",
    y="tip",
    col="time",
    hue="smoker",
    style="smoker",
    size="size",
)
```
